### ğŸ“‹ 2. Criar os Workflows

#### 2.1. `validate.yml`

Este workflow realiza a validaÃ§Ã£o do cÃ³digo, como linting, build e testes. Ele pode ser utilizado para garantir que o cÃ³digo esteja pronto para o deploy.

```yaml
# ci-modules/.github/workflows/validate.yml
name: Validate

on:
  workflow_call:

jobs:
  validate:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      - uses: actions/setup-node@v3
        with:
          node-version: '18'
      - run: npm ci
      - run: npm run lint
      - run: npm run type-check
      - run: npm run build
      - uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
        with:
          name: docusaurus-build
          path: build
